>卡莉·皮尔斯 (Carly Pearce) 和克里斯·斯塔普尔顿 (Chris Stapleton) 在 2023 年 CMA 奖红毯上与 Billboard 进行了交谈。</p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded></item><item><title>特雷西·查普曼现已成为乡村音乐协会奖获得者</title><link/>https://www.billboard.com/music/awards/tracy-chapman-2023-cma-award-winner-1235467105/<dc:creator><![CDATA[ ]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Thu, 09 Nov 2023 01:42:45 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Awards]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music]]></category><category><![CDATA[CMAs]]></category><category><![CDATA[Country]]></category><category><![CDATA[Country Music Association]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235467105 </guid><description><![CDATA["Fast Car" won song of the year thanks to Luke Combs' hit cover.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> Tracy Chapman 正式成为 CMA 获得者。这位民谣歌手兼词曲作家于 1988 年推出了代表作“Fast Car”，并在 Billboard Hot 100 排行榜上达到了第 6 位，并在周三（11 月 8 日）凭借卢克·库姆斯 (Luke Combs) 的出色表现获得了 2023 年乡村音乐协会奖热门翻唱版本在热门 100 歌曲排行榜上排名第二，并连续四个星期位居热门乡村歌曲排行榜榜首。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/themes/vip/pmc-billboard-2021/assets/public/lazyload-fallback.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/57-cma-awards-logo-2032-billboard-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="第57届CMA奖" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max"> 2023 CMA 奖项获奖名单（更新中） </h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 11/08/2023 </time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>库姆斯凭借《Fast Car》赢得 2023 年 CMA 年度单曲奖后不久，该歌曲的唯一创作者查普曼赢得了 CMA 年度歌曲奖，该奖项授予歌曲的作者。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>大奥普里大剧院的新成员萨拉·埃文斯 (Sara Evans) 站在 86 岁的乡村传奇人物比尔·安德森 (Bill Anderson) 旁边，宣读了查普曼 (Chapman) 送来的获奖感言：“很抱歉今晚我不能和你们一起参加。我的歌曲在出道 35 年后再次得到认可，真是一种荣幸。感谢 CMA，特别感谢卢克和《快车》的所有粉丝。”</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>在查普曼获胜之前，库姆斯在获奖感言中赞扬了她。 “首先，我要感谢特雷西·查普曼创作了有史以来最好的歌曲，”他在纳什维尔的普利司通体育场说道。 “我录制这首歌是因为我非常喜欢这首歌，它对我的​​一生意义重大。这是我四岁以来第一首最喜欢的歌曲。”</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>库姆斯翻唱歌曲后的几个月内，查普曼就从这首歌中<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/luke-combs-fast-car-cover-tracy-chapman-royalties/"  target="_blank"  rel="noreferrer noopener"  >赚取了约</a>50 万美元的出版版税。 </p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy" class="youtube-player" width="640" height="360" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/niyJ7JgZOeE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent" allowfullscreen="true" style="border:0;" sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation"></iframe></div></figure></div> ]]>;</content:encoded></item><item><title>保拉·阿卜杜勒 (Paula Abdul) 谈对凯莉·安德伍德 (Carrie Underwood) 和泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的喜爱、与 NKOTB 一起巡演、制作百老汇演出等 | 2023 年 CMA 奖</title><link/>https://www.billboard.com/video/paula-abdul-red-carpet-cma-awards-2023/<dc:creator><![CDATA[ ]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Thu, 09 Nov 2023 01:38:59 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Videos]]></category><category><![CDATA[Billboard]]></category><category><![CDATA[CMA Award 2023]]></category><category><![CDATA[CMA Awards]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?post_type=pmc_top_video&amp;p=1235467101 </guid><description><![CDATA[Paula Abdul chatted with Billboard on the red carpet of the 2023 CMA Awards.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-not-a-paywall"><p
